ww.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20171005005254-260407?chdtv |dead-url = no }}</ref>、[[高雄市|高雄市]]<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.storm.mg/article/191725 |title = 時代力量成立高雄黨部 黃國昌：2018每區都會有候選人 |author =  |date = 2016-11-19 |publisher = [[風傳媒|風傳媒]] |language = Zh-hant |accessdate = 2019-05-11 |quote =  |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190511162816/https://www.storm.mg/article/191725 |archive-date = 2019-05-11 |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aipl/201611190255.aspx |title = 時代力量設高雄黨部 議員選舉不缺席 |author = 王淑芬 |date = 2016-11-19 |publisher = [[中央通訊社|中央通訊社]] |language = Zh-hant |accessdate = 2019-05-11 |quote =  |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190511162816/https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aipl/201611190255.aspx |archive-date = 2019-05-11 |dead-url = no }}</ref>、[[宜蘭縣|宜蘭縣]]<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2017-10-22/101294 |title = 時力宜蘭黨部成立 自勉「治大國若烹小鮮」 |author = 鍾桂名 |date = 2017-10-22 |publisher = [[新頭殼|新頭殼]] |language = Zh-hant |accessdate = 2019-05-11 |quote =  |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190511162818/https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2017-10-22/101294 |archive-date = 2019-05-11 |dead-url = no }}</ref>、[[花蓮縣|花蓮縣]]等地區拓展，成立地方黨部<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20160703003525-260407?chdtv |title = 時代力量花東黨部成立 盼東部民眾加入改革隊伍 |author = 楊漢聲 |date = 2016-07-03 |publisher = [[中時電子報|中時電子報]] |language = Zh-hant |accessdate = 2019-05-11 |quote =  |archive-date = 2021-10-12 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211012133535/https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20160703003525-260407?chdtv |dead-url = no }}</ref>，希望透過地方黨部經營組織基層、培養人才<ref name = "楊淳卉 01"/><ref name = "陳佩君 01">{{Cite web |url = https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2018-11-13/165900 |title = 大選倒數11天》倒數拚陸戰！黃國昌要帶領黨改變地方舊政治 |author = 陳佩君 |date = 2018-11-13 |publisher = [[新頭殼|新頭殼]] |language = Zh-hant |accessdate = 2019-05-11 |quote =  |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190512062408/https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2018-11-13/165900 |archive-date = 2019-05-12 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。地方黨部還負責主要提名人的審核、調查與討論，並把名單彙整至提名小組<ref name = "周思宇 03">{{Cite web |url = https://www.storm.mg/article/355966 |title = 搶攻2018議員席次 時代力量：以六都、新竹成立黨團、發展組織為目標 |author = 周思宇 |date = 2017-11-08 |publisher = [[風傳媒|風傳媒]] |language = Zh-hant |accessdate = 2019-05-11 |quote =  |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190512110956/https://www.storm.mg/article/355966 |archive-date = 2019-05-12 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。在議題操作上，時代力量的大方向是主攻市政及議會的失能，並在各選舉區、地方上連接在地議題<ref name = "陳佩君 01"/>，例如由宜蘭縣、[[基隆市|基隆市]]、新北市議員參選人討論[[深澳發電廠|深澳發電廠]]的環境影響評估<ref name = "周思宇 02"/>。

在2018年地方公職選舉中，時代力量公布《縣市議員候選人共同公約》<ref name = "黃信維 01">{{Cite web |url = https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20171108/1237253/ |title = 時代力量搶攻2018議員選舉　拚「六都、新竹」成立黨團 |author = 黃信維 |date = 2017-11-08 |publisher = 《[[蘋果日報_(台灣)|蘋果日報]]》 |language = Zh-hant |accessdate = 2019-05-11 |quote =  |archive-date = 2020-06-14 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200614052008/https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20171108/1237253/ |dead-url = no }}</ref>，希望個人政見主張不違背其從政精神<ref name = "周思宇 03"/>。時代力量以「全國性政策」拉抬聲勢<ref name = "周思宇 01"/>，透過該次選舉發展組織<ref name = "周思宇 03"/>。其目標是在6個[[直轄市_(中華民國)|直轄市]]與新竹市等地議會成立自己的黨團<ref name = "黃信維 01"/><ref name = "周思宇 03"/><ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.peoplenews.tw/news/28d4f9ba-b2f3-4ab3-8139-3cf3e1f432b4 |title = 時代力量公布選舉辦法與公約：盼六都、竹市能成立黨團 |author = 鍾孟軒 |date = 2017-11-08 |publisher = [[民報_(2014年)|民報]] |language = Zh-hant |accessdate = 2019-05-11 |quote =  |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190512110954/https://www.peoplenews.tw/news/28d4f9ba-b2f3-4ab3-8139-3cf3e1f432b4 |archive-date = 2019-05-12 |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aipl/201810190271.aspx |title = 時代力量攻議會席次 拚都會區成立黨團 |author = 王承中和范正祥 |date = 2018-10-19 |publisher = [[中央通訊社|中央通訊社]] |language = Zh-hant |accessdate = 2019-05-11 |quote =  |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190512130357/https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aipl/201810190271.aspx |archive-date = 2019-05-12 |dead-url = no }}</ref>，將立法院的問政風格深入地方議會<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.cmmedia.com.tw/home/articles/8078 |title = 將改變帶入地方！時代力量21位議員參選人首亮相 |author = 薛如真 |date = 2018-01-20 |publisher = [[信傳媒|信傳媒]] |language = Zh-hant |accessdate = 2019-05-11 |quote =  |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190512062409/https://www.cmmedia.com.tw/home/articles/8078 |archive-date = 2019-05-12 |dead-url = no }}</ref>，改變腐敗的[[中華民國政治|舊政治文化]]<ref name = "陳佩君 01"/>。時代力量主要以[[Facebook|Facebook]]等[[社群媒體|社群媒體]]網站宣傳，並精準設定「受眾」來獲得最大效益<ref name = "周思宇 02"/>，其鮮明設計的文宣亦備受注目<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/china/2016/01/160113_taiwan_election_campaigns_social-media |title = 台灣大選：社交媒體上的選舉文宣戰 |author = 鄭仲嵐 |date = 2016-01-13 |publisher = [[英國廣播公司新聞網|英國廣播公司新聞網]] |language = Zh-hant |accessdate = 2019-05-11 |quote =  |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190512114704/https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/china/2016/01/160113_taiwan_election_campaigns_social-media |archive-date = 2019-05-12 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。為了強化辨識度，時代力量還外聘視覺導演、影像團隊，合作處理視覺表現<ref name = "周思宇 02"/>。

作為提倡透明、開放、參與式的政黨，時代力量邀請所有認同理念的民眾加入<ref name = "陳慧萍 01"/>。候選人在正式接受時代力量提名前，必須具備有效黨員身分，且無[[多重國籍|多重國籍]]或[[永久居留權|永久居留權]]<ref name = "周思宇 03"/>。最初時代力量的黨章規定黨員年齡為15歲以上，但因為《政黨法》的規定，修改成需要年滿16歲以上<ref name = "李秉芳 01"/>。截至2018年12月31日，具備完整資格的黨員總數有2,238人<ref name = "范正祥 02">{{Cite web |url = https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aipl/201901050082.aspx |title = 時力12日黨員大會 下屆黨主席最快2月產生 |author = 范正祥 |date = 2016-01-31 |publisher = [[中央通訊社|中央通訊社]] |language = Zh-hant |accessdate = 2019-05-11 |quote =  |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190512033819/https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aipl/201901050082.aspx |archive-date = 2019-05-12 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。時代力量的成員大多是長期參與婦女、環保、司法改革、人權等領域的社會運動，並深度參與太陽花學運<ref name = "林怡廷 02"/>。

